dct_description_sm: Front of brochure published by the New Jersey Department of Conservation and Economic Development of Lebanon (now Brendan T. Byrne State Forest. Front includes a table of campsites available and descriptions of the bathing facilities, cabin and boat rentals and hunting and fishing areas. Three photographic illustrations.
